extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.EObjectImpl
implements CHRtSpecification
    An implementation of the model object 'CH Rt Specification'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Part With Port
    • WCET
    • Local WCET
    • Relative Priority
    • Ceiling
    • Memory Size Footprint
    • Stack Size
    • Heap Size
    • Slot
    • Base Comment
    • Occ Kind
    • Protection
    • Rl Dl
    • Context
    • Resp T
    • Block T
    • Operation Req For Sporadic Occ
